data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style home, ideally situated on a spacious, flat lot in the heart of Soddy Daisy. Boasting a durable and stylish metal roof, this property combines timeless design with practical living.Located in a friendly Soddy Daisy neighborhood, this home is just minutes away from local schools, parks, shopping, and dining options, combining the tranquility of suburban living with the convenience of city amenities.Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful ranch-style house your new home. Schedule a viewing today and experience all that this Soddy Daisy gem has to offer!
